-spec count_servers(integer(), [[integer()]], integer(), [integer()]) -> [integer()].
count_servers(N, Logs, X, Queries) ->
    SortedLogs = lists:sort(fun([_, T1], [_, T2]) -> T1 < T2 end, Logs),
    lists:map(
        fun(Query) ->
            ActiveServers = lists:foldl(
                fun([Server, Time], Acc) ->
                    if
                        Time >= Query - X andalso Time =< Query ->
                            maps:put(Server, true, Acc);
                        true ->
                            Acc
                    end
                end, #{}, SortedLogs),
            N - maps:size(ActiveServers)
        end, Queries).
